Comment: 0,0:01:16.26,0:01:18.26,CN - down,,0,0,0,,OP前
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.47,0:01:23.56,CN - down,Shizuka,0,0,0,,走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.31,0:01:26.06,CN - down,Shizuka,0,0,0,,去爸爸那里
Comment: 0,0:02:23.24,0:02:25.24,CN - down,,0,0,0,,正文
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.24,0:02:28.87,CN - down,Takopi,0,0,0,,这里就是「爸爸的地方」吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.58,0:02:31.71,CN - down,Shizuka,0,0,0,,能见到的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.96,0:02:35.71,CN - down,Shizuka,0,0,0,,能见到的 能见到的 能见到的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.71,0:02:36.96,CN - down,Shizuka,0,0,0,,能见到的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.34,0:02:39.43,CN - down,Shizuka,0,0,0,,马上就能见到恰噼
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.55,0:02:44.10,CN - down,Shizuka,0,0,0,,还有爸爸
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.01,0:02:46.31,CN - down,Shizuka's Dad,0,0,0,,来啦
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.02,0:02:50.31,CN - down,Shizuka,0,0,0,,爸爸
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.73,0:02:52.52,CN - down,Shizuka's Dad,0,0,0,,欸
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.06,0:02:55.32,CN - down,Shizuka's Dad,0,0,0,,静香
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.57,0:02:58.03,CN - down,Shizuka's Dad,0,0,0,,怎么这么突然
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.03,0:02:58.99,CN - down,Shizuka,0,0,0,,爸爸
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.99,0:03:00.70,CN - down,Satsuki,0,0,0,,爸爸
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.70,0:03:02.28,CN - down,Shizuka's Dad,0,0,0,,怎么了五月
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.66,0:03:05.58,CN - down,Shizuka's Dad,0,0,0,,很危险的 绘梨她还在睡觉呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.28,0:03:05.58,CN - up,Satsuki,0,0,0,,来这边嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.58,0:03:08.33,CN - up,Satsuki,0,0,0,,呐呐 和我玩吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.58,0:03:06.70,CN - down,Shizuka,0,0,0,,爸爸
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.33,0:03:10.41,CN - down,Shizuka's Dad,0,0,0,,都说了这样很危险啦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.41,0:03:13.13,CN - up,Satsuki,0,0,0,,我不要 我要抱抱
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.83,0:03:13.13,CN - down,Shizuka,0,0,0,,爸爸
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.84,0:03:18.34,CN - down,Shizuka,0,0,0,,爸爸 我是来见恰噼的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.09,0:03:19.63,CN - up,Satsuki,0,0,0,,唔
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.63,0:03:20.51,CN - down,Shizuka's Dad,0,0,0,,恰噼
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.26,0:03:23.72,CN - down,Shizuka,0,0,0,,听 是恰噼的声音
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.26,0:03:28.81,CN - down,Shizuka,0,0,0,,不是恰噼
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.81,0:03:32.23,CN - down,Satsuki,0,0,0,,爸爸 这个女孩 是谁
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.69,0:03:33.69,CN - down,Shizuka's Dad,0,0,0,,诶
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.69,0:03:36.98,CN - down,Satsuki,0,0,0,,为什么她也叫你「爸爸」呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.23,0:03:39.99,CN - down,Shizuka's Dad,0,0,0,,啊 啊 这个啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.87,0:03:49.37,CN - down,Shizuka's Dad,0,0,0,,我也不是很懂
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.17,0:04:04.84,CN - down,Shizuka,0,0,0,,也许是那两个小孩吃掉了恰噼
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.30,0:04:10.10,CN - down,Shizuka,0,0,0,,章鱼噼不也会吃掉落蝉吗 或许就是那样
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.64,0:04:12.10,CN - down,Takopi,0,0,0,,静香
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.43,0:04:15.48,CN - down,Shizuka,0,0,0,,那么 我们要把恰噼「取出来」
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.48,0:04:16.31,CN - down,Takopi,0,0,0,,静香
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.31,0:04:18.61,CN - down,Shizuka,0,0,0,,要是调查过胃是否就能知道了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.69,0:04:20.99,CN - down,Takopi,0,0,0,,静香
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.62,0:04:30.83,CN - down,Shizuka,0,0,0,,章鱼噼
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.87,0:04:36.04,CN - down,Shizuka,0,0,0,,给我能调查被捉住人类的胃的道具吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.58,0:04:39.04,CN - down,Takopi,0,0,0,,我 我不知道啊噼
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.63,0:04:41.80,CN - down,Takopi,0,0,0,,这种道具没有噼
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.80,0:04:43.72,CN - down,Shizuka,0,0,0,,诶 你说谎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.72,0:04:44.59,CN - down,Takopi,0,0,0,,静香
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.59,0:04:47.18,CN - down,Shizuka,0,0,0,,那算了 我自己想办法
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.43,0:04:47.59,CN - up,Takopi,0,0,0,,好痛
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.76,0:04:50.97,CN - up,Takopi,0,0,0,,静香 别这样噼
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.93,0:04:53.14,CN - down,Shizuka,0,0,0,,啊 用这个就能在夜晚进去而不被发现
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.14,0:04:55.52,CN - down,Takopi,0,0,0,,静香 你听我说吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.86,0:04:59.27,CN - down,Takopi,0,0,0,,静香
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.94,0:05:02.82,CN - down,Takopi,0,0,0,,我们回去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.11,0:05:06.53,CN - down,Takopi,0,0,0,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.07,0:05:13.04,CN - down,Takopi,0,0,0,,我笨笨的 也很无能噼
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.04,0:05:17.58,CN - down,Takopi,0,0,0,,才会让静香你 努力到这么身心俱残的地步
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.58,0:05:21.50,CN - down,Takopi,0,0,0,,对不起 所以我们回家吧噼
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.88,0:05:25.55,CN - down,Takopi,0,0,0,,而且我能拿出让你快乐游玩的道具噼
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.55,0:05:28.97,CN - down,Takopi,0,0,0,,用「拍拍翅膀」稍微在空中悬浮
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.97,0:05:34.35,CN - down,Takopi,0,0,0,,用「变身调色盘」变成毛毛虫 肯定也很有趣的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.27,0:05:38.56,CN - down,Takopi,0,0,0,,我希望你能变回原来的静香噼
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.19,0:05:41.32,CN - down,Takopi,0,0,0,,我只是 希望你能笑出
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.32,0:05:42.57,CN - down,Shizuka,0,0,0,,啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.53,0:05:47.33,CN - down,Shizuka,0,0,0,,章鱼噼也 不愿帮助我了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.86,0:05:49.37,CN - down,Shizuka,0,0,0,,那就算了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.37,0:05:50.37,CN - down,Takopi,0,0,0,,啊嘞
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.12,0:05:52.58,CN - down,Takopi,0,0,0,,这双眼好像
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.54,0:05:56.66,CN - down,Takopi,0,0,0,,我曾在哪里见过
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.21,0:05:59.08,CN - down,Marina,0,0,0,,要吃吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.75,0:06:00.17,CN - up,Marina,0,0,0,,一直都是一个人
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.08,0:06:00.67,CN - down,Marina,0,0,0,,都说了 这很恶心啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.67,0:06:03.88,CN - down,Happy Mama,0,0,0,,快乐星人最为重要的「规则」被你破坏了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.50,0:06:05.59,CN - up,Marina,0,0,0,,对不起 对不起 对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.88,0:06:05.59,CN - down,Takopi,0,0,0,,我明白噼 ***酱
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.59,0:06:07.14,CN - up,Marina,0,0,0,,好讨厌一个人 但从那时就一直这样
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.89,0:06:08.39,CN - down,Happy Mama,0,0,0,,这是你的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.93,0:06:10.06,CN - down,Happy Mama,0,0,0,,「罪」
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.22,0:06:13.43,CN - down,Takopi,0,0,0,,啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.68,0:06:16.02,CN - down,Takopi,0,0,0,,对啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.11,0:06:24.69,CN - down,Takopi,0,0,0,,为什么我会忘记呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.15,0:06:29.20,CN - down,Marina,0,0,0,,啊嘞
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.78,0:06:32.83,CN - down,Marina,0,0,0,,呐 那里有什么东西在吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.28,0:06:35.29,CN - down,Marina,0,0,0,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.79,0:06:36.79,CN - down,Takopi,0,0,0,,噼
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.08,0:06:43.29,CN - down,Takopi,0,0,0,,我是快乐星人 为大家带来快乐噼
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.54,0:06:47.34,CN - down,Takopi,0,0,0,,首先我想知道噼 那个
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.80,0:06:50.72,CN - down,Takopi,0,0,0,,你的名字是
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.47,0:06:55.56,CN - down,Marina,0,0,0,,麻里奈
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.31,0:06:59.14,CN - down,Marina,0,0,0,,云母坂麻里奈
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.27,0:07:05.27,CN - down,Takopi,0,0,0,,我是快乐星人
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.57,0:07:09.90,CN - down,Takopi,0,0,0,,可以的话希望你能用「地球语言」给我起一个快乐名字
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.74,0:07:13.91,CN - down,Marina,0,0,0,,那就叫你「乐色废物」
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.12,0:07:17.91,CN - down,Student A,0,0,0,,看吧 那个人
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.91,0:07:20.08,CN - down,Student B,0,0,0,,快看 她脸上的伤疤
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.08,0:07:21.79,CN - down,Student A,0,0,0,,简直就像黑帮一样
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.79,0:07:22.96,CN - down,Student C,0,0,0,,恐怖
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.25,0:07:25.09,CN - down,Student B,0,0,0,,听说她一言不合就动手
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.09,0:07:26.46,CN - down,Student D,0,0,0,,为什么要戴着折耳根花啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.71,0:07:28.71,CN - down,Student E,0,0,0,,但是稍微有点帅气呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.17,0:07:30.47,CN - down,Takopi,0,0,0,,麻里奈
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.97,0:07:33.43,CN - down,Takopi,0,0,0,,我想报答你请我吃的饭
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.43,0:07:34.96,CN - down,Takopi,0,0,0,,这是我的快乐道具
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.96,0:07:36.14,CN - down,Marina,0,0,0,,好烦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.14,0:07:38.35,CN - down,Takopi,0,0,0,,「花朵发簪」
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.35,0:07:39.93,CN - down,Takopi,0,0,0,,用这个玩「扮花花」游戏吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.93,0:07:41.11,CN - down,Marina,0,0,0,,谁要扮啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.23,0:07:45.98,CN - down,Takopi,0,0,0,,麻里奈 这个竟然是会发出土星兔声音的圆珠笔哦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.48,0:07:51.57,CN - down,Marina,0,0,0,,喂 在家给我守点规矩啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.45,0:07:59.45,CN - down,News anchor,0,0,0,,自前些日子起启动的新冠病毒第十轮疫苗接种
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.45,0:08:03.46,CN - down,News anchor,0,0,0,,对于反复接种的加强针 社会已然浮现出一些担忧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.53,0:08:10.47,CN - up,News anchor,0,0,0,,虽然加强针是为了大幅降低重症化和住院风险而被政府推荐
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.92,0:08:16.18,CN - up,News anchor,0,0,0,,但部分专家警告 这样可能会伴随一定的副作用而需警惕
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.75,0:08:06.71,CN - down,Marina's Mom,0,0,0,,欢迎回来 麻里
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.25,0:08:09.17,CN - down,Marina,0,0,0,,妈妈
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.92,0:08:12.22,CN - down,Marina's Mom,0,0,0,,麻里
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.22,0:08:13.72,CN - down,Marina,0,0,0,,你起来了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.47,0:08:16.18,CN - down,Marina,0,0,0,,我以为你睡了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.18,0:08:17.85,CN - down,Marina,0,0,0,,我现在就去准备晚饭
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.51,0:08:18.76,CN - up,Marina's Mom,0,0,0,,我说 麻里
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.35,0:08:20.43,CN - up,Marina's Mom,0,0,0,,康普茶
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.68,0:08:23.35,CN - down,Marina,0,0,0,,抱歉我回来这么晚 今天发生了很多事
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.98,0:08:24.98,CN - down,Marina,0,0,0,,啊 康普茶吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.40,0:08:27.27,CN - down,Marina,0,0,0,,我明白了 现在给你倒
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.03,0:08:31.28,CN - down,Marina's Mom,0,0,0,,麻里
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.28,0:08:34.07,CN - down,Marina,0,0,0,,药 已经吃了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.07,0:08:36.70,CN - down,Marina,0,0,0,,听说它的副作用会做噩梦呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.70,0:08:37.83,CN - up,Marina's Mom,0,0,0,,麻里
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.95,0:08:41.20,CN - down,Marina,0,0,0,,那个 康普茶 康普茶
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.62,0:08:44.71,CN - down,Marina,0,0,0,,抱歉 已经没
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.71,0:08:45.83,CN - down,Marina's Mom,0,0,0,,都说了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.71,0:08:55.97,CN - down,Marina's Mom,0,0,0,,为 为什么不在喝完前 在网上提前订一箱啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.97,0:09:01.27,CN - down,Marina's Mom,0,0,0,,妈妈我只配喝这么便宜的酒吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.27,0:09:02.14,CN - down,Marina,0,0,0,,妈妈
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.14,0:09:07.27,CN - down,Marina's Mom,0,0,0,,呐 妈妈需要的是用红茶菌发酵的酒啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.27,0:09:08.94,CN - down,Marina's Mom,0,0,0,,麻里你也是这么想的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.94,0:09:10.32,CN - down,Marina,0,0,0,,妈妈 不是
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.86,0:09:13.40,CN - down,Marina's Mom,0,0,0,,家务事一点也都做不好
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.40,0:09:16.95,CN - down,Marina's Mom,0,0,0,,就是这样才没有男人愿意追你
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.07,0:09:16.70,CN - up,Marina,0,0,0,,对不起 妈妈
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.07,0:09:21.12,CN - down,Marina's Mom,0,0,0,,你是 想说这一切都是我的错吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.91,0:09:26.75,CN - down,Marina's Mom,0,0,0,,连你也要说是因为我母乳太少才不行吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.75,0:09:29.21,CN - down,Marina's Mom,0,0,0,,才把孩子养得这么失败吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.75,0:09:27.92,CN - up,Takopi,0,0,0,,好热闹啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.21,0:09:32.55,CN - down,Marina,0,0,0,,玻 玻璃好恐怖
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.34,0:09:34.51,CN - down,Marina,0,0,0,,玻璃
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.88,0:09:38.59,CN - down,Marina,0,0,0,,小 小时候惹妈妈生气了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.18,0:09:41.43,CN - down,Marina,0,0,0,,玻 玻璃
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.43,0:09:45.60,CN - down,Marina,0,0,0,,这伤疤 就是被碎玻璃杯割烂的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.77,0:09:48.90,CN - down,Marina,0,0,0,,玻 玻璃
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.90,0:09:49.98,CN - up,Takopi,0,0,0,,噼
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.40,0:09:50.31,CN - down,Marina,0,0,0,,玻璃
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.31,0:09:53.73,CN - down,Marina,0,0,0,,我想成为一位幸福的妈妈
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.74,0:09:58.66,CN - down,Marina,0,0,0,,生下幸福的孩子 给予幸福的养育
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.66,0:09:59.70,CN - down,Takopi,0,0,0,,噼呀
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.28,0:10:02.41,CN - down,Marina,0,0,0,,这样的话 妈妈她也一定会
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.57,0:10:02.62,CN - up,Boy,0,0,0,,今天吃的点心 非常美味
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.41,0:10:06.83,CN - down,Takopi,0,0,0,,噼 什么嘛 你在「模仿」啊噼
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.62,0:10:04.45,CN - up,Mother,0,0,0,,挺好的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.83,0:10:08.37,CN - down,Marina,0,0,0,,哈 什么
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.37,0:10:12.21,CN - down,Takopi,0,0,0,,我是说 麻里奈你每次都用力触碰我
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.21,0:10:14.96,CN - down,Takopi,0,0,0,,是在模仿妈妈呀
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.71,0:10:19.84,CN - down,Takopi,0,0,0,,人类就是这样练习如何养育孩子的呀噼
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.72,0:10:24.10,CN - down,Takopi,0,0,0,,麻里奈肯定能成为一名优秀的妈妈噼
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.10,0:10:26.56,CN - up,Boy,0,0,0,,很危险的 要注意哦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.47,0:10:28.81,CN - down,Takopi,0,0,0,,那么 我来帮助你成为母亲吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.14,0:10:30.23,CN - down,Marina,0,0,0,,哈
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.23,0:10:32.94,CN - down,Takopi,0,0,0,,首先要选一位爸爸呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.94,0:10:35.82,CN - down,Takopi,0,0,0,,我们现在一起去找爸爸吧噼
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.82,0:10:38.70,CN - down,Marina,0,0,0,,哈 不用你多管闲事
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.70,0:10:39.95,CN - down,Azuma,0,0,0,,云母坂同学
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.74,0:10:42.49,CN - down,Marina,0,0,0,,欸
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.00,0:10:53.59,CN - down,Marina,0,0,0,,然后 在夏天 小学毕业后偶遇
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.42,0:10:57.34,CN - down,Marina,0,0,0,,然后我们 不知不觉就开始交往了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.34,0:11:00.51,CN - down,Marina's Mom,0,0,0,,啊啦 这样子啊 麻里
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.51,0:11:03.60,CN - down,Marina's Mom,0,0,0,,什么嘛 要是早点告诉我就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.60,0:11:06.22,CN - down,Marina,0,0,0,,嗯 所以今后我会介绍他给你
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.22,0:11:08.23,CN - down,Marina's Mom,0,0,0,,挺好的呀 我很期待
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.68,0:11:11.73,CN - down,Marina's Mom,0,0,0,,爸爸也因为新冠疫情工作并不顺利
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.73,0:11:13.98,CN - down,Marina's Mom,0,0,0,,我想他是时候回来了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.98,0:11:16.53,CN - down,Marina's Mom,0,0,0,,到那时候 我们再在一起吃饭吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.19,0:11:18.78,CN - down,Marina,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.90,0:11:23.32,CN - down,Marina's Mom,0,0,0,,他是那家诊所的儿子吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.57,0:11:25.66,CN - down,Marina's Mom,0,0,0,,真期待他的未来呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.66,0:11:28.29,CN - down,Marina,0,0,0,,啊 这件事的话
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.29,0:11:30.21,CN - down,Azuma,0,0,0,,继承的是我哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.67,0:11:34.88,CN - down,Marina,0,0,0,,尽量不要太提及就好
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.00,0:11:40.42,CN - down,Marina,0,0,0,,但是好久没有和妈妈这么开心地聊过天了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.42,0:11:41.76,CN - down,Takopi,0,0,0,,是吗噼
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.18,0:11:47.14,CN - down,Marina,0,0,0,,真君会不会喜欢甜食呢 好像他喜欢松饼点心呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.14,0:11:49.22,CN - down,Marina,0,0,0,,今后 做给他吃吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.60,0:11:50.77,CN - down,Marina,0,0,0,,而且
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.94,0:11:55.69,CN - down,Marina,0,0,0,,伤疤的事 好像他也并不在意
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.61,0:11:55.98,CN - up,Student A,0,0,0,,自言自语
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.98,0:11:57.40,CN - up,Student B,0,0,0,,惨了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.44,0:12:02.70,CN - down,Marina,0,0,0,,我 小时候发生了很多事
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.70,0:12:05.95,CN - down,Marina,0,0,0,,爸爸离家出走 妈妈也变化很大
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.53,0:12:10.25,CN - down,Marina,0,0,0,,和我交好的朋友也没有 一直都是一个人
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.79,0:12:13.08,CN - down,Marina,0,0,0,,但是最近
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.08,0:12:15.33,CN - down,Takopi,0,0,0,,快乐黏糊吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.75,0:12:20.05,CN - down,Takopi,0,0,0,,噼
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.22,0:12:22.35,CN - down,Marina,0,0,0,,不过说实话
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.26,0:12:26.26,CN - down,Marina,0,0,0,,要不是有你 我可能不会走到那条路上
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.85,0:12:29.93,CN - down,Marina,0,0,0,,然后 就不会遇到直君
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.73,0:12:34.60,CN - down,Marina,0,0,0,,所以 怎么说呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.86,0:12:39.07,CN - down,Marina,0,0,0,,最近稍微还不错啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.03,0:12:43.11,CN - down,Marina,0,0,0,,谢谢你
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.58,0:12:52.79,CN - down,Girl A,0,0,0,,听说了吗 有转校生
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.79,0:12:53.91,CN - down,Girl B,0,0,0,,啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.91,0:12:57.71,CN - down,Girl A,0,0,0,,说是超漂亮的人 应该是本地人吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.71,0:13:00.46,CN - down,Girl B,0,0,0,,但是听说以前发生了很多事
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.46,0:13:04.39,CN - down,Girl B,0,0,0,,还记得吗 很多年之前的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.60,0:13:07.05,CN - down,Girl B,0,0,0,,她曾经自杀未遂
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.43,0:13:15.35,CN - down,Girl A,0,0,0,,欸 不是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.35,0:13:17.31,CN - down,Girl B,0,0,0,,说是绳子中途断了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.31,0:13:20.15,CN - down,Marina,0,0,0,,对不起 直君 你不喜欢吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.57,0:13:22.44,CN - down,Marina,0,0,0,,手 碰到了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.15,0:13:25.65,CN - down,Marina,0,0,0,,欸 怎么了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.66,0:13:36.25,CN - down,Azuma,0,0,0,,久世同学除了我以外再无别人了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.25,0:13:40.79,CN - down,Azuma,0,0,0,,一个人无依无靠单独回到家乡
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.79,0:13:43.42,CN - down,Azuma,0,0,0,,我认为能再见到她就是奇迹
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.76,0:13:44.88,CN - up,Girl,0,0,0,,妈妈 快点
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.17,0:13:46.63,CN - down,Azuma,0,0,0,,小学的时候 我就被她所吸引
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.18,0:13:48.93,CN - down,Azuma,0,0,0,,她只能依靠我了现在
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.43,0:13:51.89,CN - down,Azuma,0,0,0,,我也明白自己非她莫属了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.47,0:13:53.27,CN - down,Azuma,0,0,0,,所以
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.02,0:13:55.23,CN - down,Marina's Mom,0,0,0,,麻里
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.85,0:13:58.10,CN - down,Marina's Mom,0,0,0,,东君 还没有来吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.10,0:14:00.56,CN - down,Marina's Mom,0,0,0,,妈妈 好久没有做这么丰盛的晚餐啦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.15,0:14:03.48,CN - down,Marina's Mom,0,0,0,,还有麻里你喜欢的「巴伐露亚奶冻」
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.32,0:14:08.20,CN - down,Marina's Mom,0,0,0,,好期待啊 不知道他会不会喜欢呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.70,0:14:12.12,CN - down,Marina's Mom,0,0,0,,快看 妈妈久违的吹了头发呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.12,0:14:15.37,CN - down,Takopi,0,0,0,,噼 那我就去叫东君过来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.91,0:14:17.50,CN - down,Takopi,0,0,0,,等等我噼
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.92,0:14:23.30,CN - down,Azuma,0,0,0,,抱歉突然叫你出来
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.59,0:14:24.67,CN - down,Shizuka,0,0,0,,没关系
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.30,0:14:29.39,CN - down,Azuma,0,0,0,,没有什么安排吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.01,0:14:33.01,CN - down,Shizuka,0,0,0,,除了东君我也没有认识的人
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.60,0:14:36.52,CN - down,Shizuka,0,0,0,,和我搭话的人也没有
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.18,0:14:39.44,CN - down,Azuma,0,0,0,,怎么会 久世同学明明非常
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.07,0:14:46.15,CN - down,Azuma,0,0,0,,有 有魅力
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.65,0:14:53.62,CN - down,Shizuka,0,0,0,,东君才是没关系吧 是不是挺忙的 和我不一样
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.91,0:14:55.37,CN - down,Azuma,0,0,0,,那样的事
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.16,0:14:58.37,CN - down,Marina,0,0,0,,那个
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.71,0:15:02.42,CN - down,Marina,0,0,0,,直君他 说今天不能来了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.42,0:15:05.30,CN - down,Marina's Mom,0,0,0,,欸 这么突然
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.71,0:15:07.72,CN - down,Marina's Mom,0,0,0,,不过 这也没办法啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.30,0:15:12.55,CN - down,Marina's Mom,0,0,0,,下次 呐 下次呢 下次什么时候来呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.39,0:15:18.59,CN - down,Marina's Mom,0,0,0,,麻里
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.93,0:15:24.19,CN - down,Marina,0,0,0,,这个 那个 我
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.74,0:15:33.28,CN - down,Marina,0,0,0,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.66,0:15:37.29,CN - down,Azuma,0,0,0,,是我的不好
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.25,0:15:40.70,CN - down,Azuma,0,0,0,,云母坂她 肯定会受伤的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.03,0:15:44.30,CN - down,Azuma,0,0,0,,我总是半途而废
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.67,0:15:47.63,CN - down,Azuma,0,0,0,,比起润也 我也做不到他一样好
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.13,0:15:52.51,CN - down,Marina's Mom,0,0,0,,麻里 你做了什么
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.51,0:15:56.76,CN - down,Marina's Mom,0,0,0,,光沉默谁能知道你啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.39,0:16:02.65,CN - down,Marina's Mom,0,0,0,,又是 那伤疤的原因吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.02,0:16:08.32,CN - down,Marina's Mom,0,0,0,,我真是「失职母亲」啊 都怪我让你变成残缺品的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.32,0:16:08.95,CN - down,Marina,0,0,0,,不是的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.95,0:16:11.51,CN - down,Marina's Mom,0,0,0,,但是 就因这样
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.51,0:16:14.40,CN - down,Marina's Mom,0,0,0,,我今天不也好好准备了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.66,0:16:17.95,CN - down,Marina's Mom,0,0,0,,还做了这么多饭菜
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.66,0:16:23.83,CN - down,Marina,0,0,0,,直 直君 他喜欢别人了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.80,0:16:32.01,CN - down,Shizuka,0,0,0,,没关系
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.72,0:16:38.39,CN - down,Shizuka,0,0,0,,没关系的 你不用和他人比较
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.26,0:16:42.85,CN - down,Shizuka,0,0,0,,东君的「事」我都看在眼里
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.31,0:16:47.19,CN - down,Marina's Mom,0,0,0,,这样一次又一次
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.94,0:16:47.27,CN - up,Marina,0,0,0,,对不起 对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.19,0:16:49.36,CN - down,Marina's Mom,0,0,0,,你肯定也瞧不起妈妈对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.52,0:16:49.36,CN - up,Marina,0,0,0,,对不起 对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.15,0:16:52.74,CN - down,Marina's Mom,0,0,0,,麻里你也不站在我这边了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.03,0:16:55.16,CN - down,Marina's Mom,0,0,0,,明明为了你做了那么多
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.03,0:16:58.24,CN - down,Marina's Mom,0,0,0,,为什么 麻里你也这样
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.16,0:17:04.29,CN - down,Marina's Mom,0,0,0,,什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.38,0:17:08.50,CN - down,Marina's Mom,0,0,0,,难道是我的错吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.17,0:17:11.96,CN - down,Marina's Mom,0,0,0,,全部 全部
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.96,0:17:15.00,CN - down,Marina's Mom,0,0,0,,全部 全部 全部
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.30,0:17:17.55,CN - down,Marina's Mom,0,0,0,,都是我
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.03,0:17:38.28,CN - down,Takopi,0,0,0,,结果到最后还是没和他说上话呢噼
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.50,0:17:46.21,CN - down,Takopi,0,0,0,,麻里奈
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.88,0:17:51.38,CN - down,Takopi,0,0,0,,麻里奈 我回来啦噼
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.84,0:17:56.13,CN - down,Takopi,0,0,0,,抱歉噼 我没能把东君带过来
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.13,0:17:59.47,CN - down,Takopi,0,0,0,,和他在一起的人感觉眼神很恐怖
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.47,0:18:03.68,CN - up,Marina,0,0,0,,对不起对不起对不起对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.85,0:18:03.68,CN - down,Takopi,0,0,0,,好可怕噼 麻里奈你在做什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.68,0:18:04.98,CN - down,Marina,0,0,0,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.93,0:18:07.27,CN - down,Marina,0,0,0,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.40,0:18:12.27,CN - down,Marina,0,0,0,,小学四年级的时候 就得把她杀了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.07,0:18:14.53,CN - down,Marina,0,0,0,,杀了久世静香
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.86,0:18:19.37,CN - down,Marina,0,0,0,,这样的话 不仅是爸爸还有直君 都能在一起的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.33,0:18:22.16,CN - down,Marina,0,0,0,,呐
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.91,0:18:26.33,CN - down,Marina,0,0,0,,妈妈 不要丢下我一人
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.33,0:18:27.79,CN - down,Takopi,0,0,0,,麻里奈
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.42,0:18:37.38,CN - down,Marina,0,0,0,,为什么啊 你还在这啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.80,0:18:39.09,CN - down,Takopi,0,0,0,,麻里奈
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.64,0:18:42.51,CN - down,Marina,0,0,0,,什么啊 为什么这样
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.22,0:18:49.65,CN - down,Marina,0,0,0,,要早知道是这样就为你取个名字了 呐
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.65,0:18:50.97,CN - down,Takopi,0,0,0,,我明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.53,0:18:58.49,CN - down,Takopi,0,0,0,,杀了她就行了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.11,0:19:02.53,CN - down,Takopi,0,0,0,,小学四年级 久世静香
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.53,0:19:06.37,CN - down,Takopi,0,0,0,,只要杀了她 就能让你「快乐」了噼
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.83,0:19:09.83,CN - down,Takopi,0,0,0,,用大快乐时钟很简单就能做到噼
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.29,0:19:13.13,CN - down,Takopi,0,0,0,,交给我吧 等等我噼
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.59,0:19:17.17,CN - down,Takopi,0,0,0,,拜拜
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.14,0:19:29.11,CN - down,Marina,0,0,0,,哈
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.77,0:19:33.77,CN - down,Marina,0,0,0,,果然要是给祂起个名字就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.53,0:19:37.78,CN - down,Marina,0,0,0,,章鱼噼
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.49,0:19:39.32,CN - down,Marina,0,0,0,,什么的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.95,0:19:49.41,CN - down,Happian A,0,0,0,,帮我摘下快乐果实噼
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.41,0:19:50.50,CN - down,Happian B,0,0,0,,来噼
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.50,0:19:52.50,CN - down,Happian A,0,0,0,,谢谢你噼
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.00,0:19:57.13,CN - down,Takopi,0,0,0,,所以妈妈
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.13,0:20:00.88,CN - down,Takopi,0,0,0,,用这个大快乐时钟 回到小学四年级
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.88,0:20:03.43,CN - down,Takopi,0,0,0,,把久世静香杀了噼
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.64,0:20:11.10,CN - down,Happy Mama,0,0,0,,我明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.94,0:20:12.85,CN - down,Takopi,0,0,0,,噼
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.48,0:20:16.39,CN - down,Happy Mama,0,0,0,,若这是你的答案的话
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.39,0:20:17.90,CN - down,Takopi,0,0,0,,噼噼
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.69,0:20:21.61,CN - down,Happy Mama,0,0,0,,我会消除你的全部记忆
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.61,0:20:24.87,CN - down,Happy Mama,0,0,0,,让你回到刚出生时的快乐状态吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.20,0:20:28.79,CN - down,Happy Mama,0,0,0,,你一个人 来到这里
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.41,0:20:33.33,CN - down,Happy Mama,0,0,0,,破坏了快乐星球最为重要的「规则」
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.12,0:20:36.96,CN - down,Happy Mama,0,0,0,,不被允许再次返回这颗行星
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.25,0:20:41.80,CN - down,Happy Mama,0,0,0,,正因如此 你需要「重生」
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.76,0:20:46.01,CN - down,Happy Mama,0,0,0,,忘记一切
